of	O
the	O
continuous	O
speech	O
.	O
The	O
tokens	O
move	O
from	O
the	O
root	O
to	O
nodes	O
to	O
leaves	O
.	O
Hence	O
,	O
the	O
tokens	O
are	O
propagated	O
within	O
words	O
so	O
that	O
a	O
path	O
history	O
is	O
