form	O
or	O
a	O
tokens	O
link	O
form	O
.	O
The	O
tokens	O
travel	O
back	O
to	O
the	O
root	O
again	O
until	O
all	O
phones	O
have	O
been	O
recognized	O
.	O
A	O
matching	O
probability	O
is	O
calculated	O
for	O
all	O
possible	O
tokens	O
and	O
then	O
a	O
best	O
token	O
is	O
chosen	O
to	O
recognize	O
the	O
meaning	O
of	O
the	O
continuous	O
speech	O
.	O

